ordinates.\n../2574-8f806a45/docs/DEVELOPING.md:279:- Generate dynamic access coverage report: `./gradlew generateDynamicAccessCoverageReport -Pcoordinates=[group:artifact:version|k/n|all]`\n../2574-8f806a45/docs/DEVELOPING.md:280:  Output: `metadata/<group>/<artifact>/<version>/test/build/reports/dynamic-access/dynamic-access-coverage.json`\n../2574-8f806a45/docs/DEVELOPING.md:282:- Coverage (single lib): `./gradlew jacocoTestReport -Pcoordinates=[group:artifact:version|k/n|all]`\n../2574-8f806a45/stats/org.eclipse.aether/aether-spi/1.0.2.v20150114/stats.json:6:      \"coverageRatio\" : 1.0,\n../2574-8f806a45/stats/org.slf4j/slf4j-nop/1.5.3/stats.json:7:          \"coverageRatio\" : 1.0,\n../2574-8f806a45/stats/org.slf4j/slf4j-nop/1.5.3/stats.json:12:      \"coverageRatio\" : 1.0,\n../2574-8f806a45/tests/src/org.slf4j/slf4j-jdk14/1.5.6/src/test/java/org_slf4j/slf4j_jdk14/StaticMarkerBinderTest.java:23:        Marker marker = markerFactory.getMarker(\"coverage-marker\");\n../2574-8f806a45/tests/src/org.slf4j/slf4j-jdk14/1.5.6/src/test/java/org_slf4j/slf4j_jdk14/StaticMarkerBinderTest.java:28:        assertThat(marker.getName()).isEqualTo(\"coverage-marker\");\n../2574-8f806a45/tests/src/org.slf4j/slf4j-jdk14/1.5.6/src/test/java/org_slf4j/slf4j_jdk14/StaticMarkerBinderTest.java:29:        assertThat(markerFactory.getMarker(\"coverage-marker\")).isSameAs(marker);\n../2574-8f806a45/stats/org.eclipse.aether/aether-impl/1.0.2.v20150114/stats.json:7:          \"coverageRatio\" : 1.0,\n../2574-8f806a45/stats/org.eclipse.aether/aether-impl/1.0.2.v20150114/stats.json:12:      \"coverageRatio\" : 1.0,\n../2574-8f806a45/stats/org.slf4j/slf4j-jdk14/1.5.6/stats.json:7:          \"coverageRatio\" : 1.0,\n../2574-8f806a45/stats/org.slf4j/slf4j-jdk14/1.5.6/stats.json:12:      \"coverageRatio\" : 1.0,\n../2574-8f806a45/stats/com.squareup.okio/okio/1.17.2/stats.json:7:          \"coverageRatio\" : 1.0,\n../2574-8f806a45/stats/com.squareup.okio/okio/1.17.2/stats.json:12:      \"covera